# Mango chicken by Henning

![Mango_chicken](https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mango-chicken-4.jpg)

## Ingredients

- 1 Mango
- 500 g Chicken
- Rice
- Mango chutney (half of a can)
- 5 dl creme fraiche
- 3 msk soya
- 2 tsk sambal oelek
- 1 red paprika

## Preparation
Fry the chicken in a pan until white and add the soya

Add the creme fraiche, mango chutney and sambal oelek, then let it slightly boil for a few minutes

Start boiling the rice in a separat caserol

Chop the paprika and mango into pieces

At the end add the paprika and mango

Serve with indian beer like Cobra!
